column2:
"Not bad, Loser. You may be Loser the Force
to me, but you're actually not as awful as I'd
thought you'd be. Well, sort of."

"But from where I stand, you look like you're
about fourth from the bottom in ARKS, right?"

"Keep it up. Maybe next time you can
make it all the way up to fifth from the
bottom in techniques. Loser."
